msgctxt "56"
msgid "How to Play Shoot-Out:"
msgstr "Cómo jugar Shoot-Out:"

msgctxt "68"
msgid "In Shoot-Out, the score for the numbers you hit are added up."
msgstr "En el Shoot-Out, se suman los puntos de los números que aciertes."

msgctxt "80"
msgid "When all rounds are concluded, the player with the higher score is declared the winner."
msgstr "When all rounds are concluded, the player with the higher score is declared the winner."

msgctxt "92"
msgid "Scores for Shoot-Out are calculated differently than in regular darts.\\r\n"
"Sections other than bull's-eye:\\r\n"
"\\r\n"
"Number that was hit\\r\n"
"\\r\n"
"×\\r\n"
"(Single: 1, Double: 2, Triple: 3)\\r\n"
"×\\r\n"
"Number of sections hit (other than bull's-eye)\\r\n"
"Bull's-eye:\\r\n"
"\\r\n"
"\\r\n"
"(Outer Bull: 25, Inner Bull: 50)\\r\n"
"\\r\n"
"×\\r\n"
"Number of sections hit (other than bull's-eye)"
msgstr "En el Shoot-Out, los puntos se calculan diferente a los dardos normales.\\r\n"
"Para secciones que no son la diana:\\r\n"
"\\r\n"
"Número al que le atinaste\\r\n"
"\\r\n"
"×\\r\n"
"(Simple: 1, Doble: 2, Triple: 3)\\r\n"
"×\\r\n"
"Número de secciones acertadas (sin contar la diana)\\r\n"
"Diana:\\r\n"
"\\r\n"
"\\r\n"
"(Anillo exterior: 25, Centro: 50)\\r\n"
"\\r\n"
"×\\r\n"
"Número de secciones acertadas (sin contar la diana)"

msgctxt "104"
msgid "If you still have rounds remaining after hitting all of the numbers, you can continue to target the bull's-eye until you run out of rounds."
msgstr "Si te quedan rondas después de acertar todos los números, puedes seguir lanzando a la diana hasta que se acaben las rondas."

msgctxt "116"
msgid "Have fun and give it your all."
msgstr "Diviértete y da lo mejor de ti."

